The [[:en:Shinsen Shōjiroku|Shinsen Shōjiroku]], entry for the Kibi no Omi lineage in the Imperial branch of the Right Capital, describes Mitomowake as the grandson of {{ill|Wakatakehiko|ja|稚武彦命|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wakatakehiko|qq=}}.{{Sfn|御友別（古代氏族）|2010th year }}

